{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8943e56101","title":"毛泽东关于大批判的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"77bfaa4665","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"8943e56101"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bf581cd400","type":"title","text":"关于大批判的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8943e56101"},{"id":"078d648d4b","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8943e56101"},{"id":"db44d38f42","type":"paragraph","text":"大批判要慎重，要确实，要调查清楚。调查清楚，批判才有力量，否则就会一风吹。引他（指刘少奇）的话不能只顾头不顾尾。批判要站得住。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8943e56101"},{"id":"0fac6231d5","type":"paragraph","text":"“托拉斯”这个名词，不能一概驳，主要驳他走资本主义道路。有些旧名词要赋予新的意义。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8943e56101"},{"id":"fb85472bfc","type":"paragraph","text":"“驯服工具论”要批判，但也要有无产阶级纪律。服从、团结，那是有条件的。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8943e56101"},{"id":"4f38b5810c","type":"paragraph","text":"今年形势好，布、粮还是要抓。社论要搞快一些。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8943e56101"},{"id":"33821569a9","type":"paragraph","text":"批判文章文字要短。一、二千字，写一个问题，一个问题说明了就行，不能超过三千字。长了没有人看，看了也记不清。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8943e56101"},{"id":"283a7fb87c","type":"paragraph","text":"彭、罗、陆、杨可以称为“反革命修正主义分子”，其他人称“修正主义分子”。“中国的赫鲁晓夫”，文章中提，在标题上不要提。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8943e56101"}],"page":{"id":"d8c6e9818e","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8943e56101","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}